# Reorganize

You can activate a re-organize state to let your users re-organize it.

    var dashboard = fluanceDashboard.get('simple-demo');
    dashboard.toggleSortable();

You can test is dashboard is sorting :

    if (dashboard.isStateSorting) {
        // execute code if sorting mode is activated
    }

